source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Stop recording and save

Usage: bl record stop [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -o, --output <output>  Output file path (default: record.zip)
  -v, --verbose          Enable debug logging
      --headless         Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json             Output as JSON
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  bl record stop
  # Save recording to record.zip

  bl record stop -o my-recording.zip
  # Save recording to custom path
